summary: You can now have more company in breezehome.
descriptionHtml: In this mod you will have a new roommate but this isn\'t a usual roommate its a giant he just chills in breezehome with you and is also a faithful companion. I made this mod because i know people have been making changes to breezhome and i wanted to make a house friendly giant. Hope you guys enjoyyy...
author: skymodder
